replies.body:
Riot don't be hypocrites...banning Tyler1 whilst you allow Kaceytron and Nicktron continue to ruin the community for so long now. Why don't you do the same thing for them? Those are bad members (if we can call those two that) of the LoL community. If you are going to show rough Justice on players of this game, be balanced and show it to all. As I said, Kaceytron and Nicktron are still playing this game and yet you've done absolutely nothing agaisn't them. Yet you ban Tyler1? Hypocrisy!

And let me be clear Kacey and Nick are NOT the only horrible members of this game. As stated above...be balanced when it comes to rough Justice. Not just on one person. That's pathetic.

Riot you just opened Pandora's Box....get ready for all the outrage. You want to truly get rid of the bad people of this community you shall start by changing many things. The community of this game is one of the worst I've been in. And no I am not a saint. I have been reported, yes, like many of us have. But the community as a whole is not bad but those very few trollers and just plain stupid people are ruining this game for the whole. GG WP{{champion:119}}
